CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper September 23, 1961, pg. 16, reads: "Honeymooners - Mr. and Mrs. Morris Redmond of Cleveland, Ohio, were among the out-of-towners taking in festivities at Loendi Club, last week. The happy pair, who were visiting Mr. and Mrs. L. Redmond on Webster Ave., were recently married and still are on their honeymoon. - Harris photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Redmond and Morris Redmond, on their honeymoon from Cleveland, Ohio, posed at table in Loendi Club
